00:51:38.075 --> 00:51:40.411
Nasaan na yung tape na ni-record mo tungkol sa kanya?

00:51:41.829 --> 00:51:44.331
Kung may ganoong bagay, malamang
meron ka na niyan.

00:51:45.290 --> 00:51:47.000
Nalagpasan na ninyo

00:51:48.127 --> 00:51:50.170
